503/http://movie.daum.net/filmFestival/RedCarpetRead.do?ffId=19&articleId=1369327 |date=March 20, 2012 }} (in Korean). Newsen via [[Daum Communications|Daum]]. September 6, 2008.</ref>\n|-\n| Korea Fashion & Design Awards || Fashion Icon Award || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n|\n|-\n| 2008 || 1st Korea Jewelry Awards || Sapphire Award || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2009 || rowspan=2| [[2009 SBS Drama Awards|SBS Drama Awards]] || Top 10 Stars || rowspan=2| ''[[The City Hall (TV series)|City Hall]]'' || {{won}} \n|rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|author=Ko Jae-wan|title=Jang Seo-hee wins grand prize at SBS Drama Awards|url=http://www.asiae.co.kr/news/view.htm?idxno=2010010415421214182|work=10Asia|accessdate=|date=January 10, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| Excellence Award, Actor in a Drama Special || {{won}} \n|-\n| 2010 || 5th Asia Model Festival Awards || Asia Special Award, Film category || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n|\n|-\n| rowspan=11|2011 || 1st [[Cable TV Hong Kong#1st Cable TV Awards|Hong Kong Cable TV Awards]] || Best Actor || ''[[The City Hall (TV series)|City Hall]]'' || {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2| 5th [[Mnet 20's Choice Awards]] || Hot Male Body (Best Six-Pack) || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n| rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/07/07/2011070702359.html|title=\ucc28\uc2b9\uc6d0-\uacf5\ud6a8\uc9c4, 20's \ucd08\uc774\uc2a4 \ub098\ub780\ud788 2\uad00\uc655\u2026'\ucd5c\uace0\uc0ac' \uc778\uae30 \uc2e4\uac10|date= July 7, 2011|work=Chosun|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| Hot Drama Star - Male || ''[[The Greatest Love]]'' || {{won}} \n|-\n| 4th [[Style Icon Awards]] || Style Icon of the Year || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hancinema.net/cha-seung-won-the-best-icon-of-2011-34949.html|title=Cha Seung-won \"The Best Icon of 2011\"|date=November 3, 2011|work=Hancinema|publisher=Nate}}</ref>\n|-\n| 9th Korea Lifestyle Awards || Best Dressed of the Year - Male || {{NA}} || {{won}} \n|<ref>[http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?new