{"title_page": "Mitko Plahov", "text_new": "{{short description|Bulgarian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Mitko Plahov\n| image               = \n| image_size          = \n| fullname            = Mitko Kirilov Plahov\n| birth_date          = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1993|2|12}}\n| birth_place         = [[Haskovo]], Bulgaria\n| height              = {{height|m=1.78}}\n| position            = [[Midfielder]] \n| youthyears1    =  | youthclubs1    = \n| years1 = 2012\u20132015 | clubs1 = [[PFC Haskovo|Haskovo]]                         | caps1 = 51 | goals1 = 2\n| years2 = 2015\u20132016 | clubs2 = [[FC Vereya|Vereya]]                            | caps2 = 21 | goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2016\u20132017 | clubs3 = [[SFC Etar Veliko Tarnovo|Etar Veliko Tarnovo]] | caps3 = 18 | goals3 = 1\n| years4 = 2017\u20132019 | clubs4 = [[FC Arda Kardzhali|Arda Kardzhali]]            | caps4 = 20 | goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2019\u2013     | clubs5 = [[FC Botev Galabovo|Botev Galabovo]]            | caps5 = 8  | goals5 = 0\n| nationalyears1 =  | nationalteam1  =  | nationalcaps1  =  | nationalgoals1 = \n| currentclub         = [[FC Botev Galabovo|Botev Galabovo]]\n| clubnumber          = 21\n| club-update         = {{date|2019-12-15}}\n| nationalteam-update = \n}}\n\n'''Mitko Plahov''' ({{lang-bg|\u041c\u0438\u0442\u043a\u043e \u041f\u043b\u0430\u0445\u043e\u0432}}; born 12 February 1993)  is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who currently plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[FC Botev Galabovo|Botev Galabovo]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[sportal.bg]]|title=Mitko Plahov Facts|url=http://www.sportal.bg/statistics_player.php?season=105&champ=26&team=239&player=12859|language=Bulgarian}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\n\n===Haskovo===\nPlahov is youth player of [[PFC Haskovo|Haskovo]] and played in A Group with the team in the [[2014\u201315 A Group|2014\u201315]] season.\n\n===Vereya===\nOn 11 July 2015 he signed with the Bulgaria [[B PFG|B Group]] team [[FC Vereya|Vereya Stara Zagora]] coming from [[PFC Haskovo|Haskovo]].<ref>[http://dariknews.bg/view_article.php?article_id=1451947 \u0424\u041a \"\u0412\u0435\u0440\u0435\u044f\" \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0432\u043b\u0435\u0447\u0435 \u043f\u0435\u0442\u0438\u043c\u0430 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438 \u0444\u0443\u0442\u0431\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438]</ref> He made his professional debut for the league on 25 July 2015 in a 4:0 win against [[FC Septemvri Simitli|Septemvri Simitli]].<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/07/25/bulgaria/b-pfg/vereya-stara-zagora/septemvri-simitli/2057588/ Vereya vs Septemvri]</ref>\n\n===Arda Kardzhali===\nOn 21 June 2017, after a season in [[SFC Etar Veliko Tarnovo|Etar Veliko Tarnovo]], he joined [[Third Amateur Football League (Bulgaria)|Third League]] club [[FC Arda Kardzhali|Arda Kardzhali]].<ref>{{cite web | title = \u0410\u0440\u0434\u0430 (\u041a\u044a\u0440\u0434\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438) \u043e\u0431\u044f\u0432\u0438 7 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0447\u0438, \u043a\u0430\u043a\u0442\u043e \u0438 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0437\u0430 \u043b\u044f\u0442\u043d\u0430\u0442\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u0433\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0432\u043a\u0430 | url = http://sportove.net/140327/ | publisher = sportove.net | date = 21 June 2017 | language = Bulgarian}}</ref>\n==Career statistics==\n\n===Club===\n{{updated| 18 January 2016 }}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!Colspan=\"3\"|Club performance!!Colspan=\"2\"|League!!Colspan=\"2\"|Cup!!Colspan=\"2\"|Continental!!Colspan=\"2\"|Other!!Colspan=\"3\"|Total\n|-\n!Club!!League!!Season!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n!Colspan=\"3\"|Bulgaria!!Colspan=\"2\"|League!!Colspan=\"2\"|[[Bulgarian Cup]]!!Colspan=\"2\"|[[UEFA|Europe]]!!Colspan=\"2\"|Other<ref group=lower-alpha>Includes [[Bulgarian Supercup]] matches.</ref>!!Colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"center\"|[[PFC Haskovo|Haskovo]]\n| rowspan=\"1\"|[[V AFG|V Group]]\n|[[2012\u201313 V AFG|2012\u201313]]\n|20||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||20||0\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|[[B PFG|B Group]]\n|[[2013\u201314 A Group|2013\u201314]]\n|24||2||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||26||2\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"|[[A PFG|A Group]]\n|[[2014\u201315 A Group|2014\u201315]]\n|7||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||8||0\n|-\n! colspan=2 | Total\n! 51 !! 2 !! 3 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 54 !! 2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"center\"|[[FC Vereya|Vereya Stara Zagora]]\n| rowspan=\"1\"|[[Bulgarian B Professional Football Group|B Group]]\n|[[2015\u201316 B Group|2015\u201316]]\n|16||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||17||0\n|-\n! colspan=2 | Total\n! 16 !! 0 !! 1 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 17 !! 0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career statistics !! 67 !! 2 !! 4 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 0 !! 71 !! 2\n|}\n{{Reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|mitko-plahov/307587}}\n\n{{FC Botev Galabovo squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Plahov, Mitko}}\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n[[Category:FC Haskovo players]]\n[[Category:FC Vereya players]]\n[[Category:SFC Etar Veliko Tarnovo players]]\n[[Category:FC Arda Kardzhali players]]\n[[Category:FC Botev Galabovo players]]\n\n{{Bulgaria-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Mitko Plahov\n| image               = \n| image_size          = \n| fullname            = Mitko Kirilov Plahov\n| birth_date          = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1993|2|12}}\n| birth_place         = [[Haskovo]], Bulgaria\n| height              = {{height|m=1.78}}\n| position            = [[Midfielder]] \n| youthyears1    =  | youthclubs1    = \n| years1 = 2012\u201320